@Google Hey the new Slices feature for the settings app on the Pixel 3 has a bit of an issue.

If you search for "Wi-Fi" or "Wi Fi" the slice shows up, but the more common spelling of "WiFi" doesn't trigger the slice to show up.

Just a heads up!

